name: Incompatible Species Episode 6: Incomprehensible Interlude
description:
In this, the penultimate episode, the group ducks out into the woods for the night, but the day doesn't end in calm when Chris and Lucius decide to unearth their past. Little does most of the Exterminator group know that something much more sinister has been slowly blooming to germination.

This is a standalone release for the sixth episode of Incompatible Species: Incomprehensible Interlude. You can find the full compilation of releases up to now here: https://poxnixles.itch.io/incomspe
